* to list remote branches
git branch -r

* to download specific remote branch
git checkout -t origin/control-flow

* continue
to ignore or skip code for certain values
increment needs to done before

* tip-1
summer ? 45 : 35;

* tip-2
return number > 0 && number % 2 != 0;

* tip-3
int upperLimit = summer ? 45 : 35; -> means if summer is true upperLimit equals to 45, otherwise equals to 35.
return temperature = 25 && temperature <= upperLimit; -> means return true if conditions are met.

* tip-4
declare variables in the narrowest scope possible
declare and initialize variables in the same place if possible
